### MESSAGING ENDPOINTS (2 tests)
### ============================================

### Test 27: Get Conversation Messages
# Replace {startupId}, {userId}, {otherUserId} with actual IDs
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversation/{startupId}/{userId}/{otherUserId}?page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Test 28: Get All Conversations (Inbox)
# Replace {startupId}, {userId} with actual IDs
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversations/{startupId}/{userId}?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### INTERESTS & INVITATIONS (4 tests)
### ============================================

### Test 29: Get Received Interests (Founder)
# Replace {founderId} with actual founder ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/interests/received/{founderId}?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Test 30: Get Sent Interests (Talent)
# Replace {talentId} with actual talent ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/interests/sent/{talentId}?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Test 31: Get Sent Invitations (Founder)
# Replace {founderId} with actual founder ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/invitations/sent/{founderId}?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}
